storage_model

Class Storage

  • java.lang.Object
    • storage_model.Storage

  • public class Storage
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the main storage container for the application, holding inside both trailStorage and userStorage. I made this purely for organizational purpose and ease of access when using backup and restore. This class contains common methods such as getters and setters.
    Author:
    Nick Broome
